Greetings,
as https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/24339, adding the Hybrid Format SiStrip Zero Suppression algorithms for 2018 PbPb data-taking, has recently been merged in the 10.3.X branch, this PR packages into a RelVal wofkflow the steps for:
   * taking as input the 2015 PbPb `VirginRaw` data;
   * hybrid emulation (with ZS10 repacking);
   * HLT-like zero-suppression of hybridized input (with normal ZS repacking);
   * standard RECO of the repacked out;

The 3 steps have been taken from https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/24339#issuecomment-418740678.

FYI @echabert @pieterdavid @icali @CesarBernardes
